                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990508-26-off154 t17990508-26-cd155"></join>, a cloth coat, value 20s. a waistcoat, value 10s. a pair of breeches, value 10s. a pair of drawers, value 1s. a pair of silver knee-buckles, value 3s. a metal watch, value 40s. a metal acron, value 1d. a watch key, value 1d. and a cotton shawl, value 3d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
